title: Wireless Network Watcher 1.91
description:
Wireless Network Watcher 1.91

image

Size: 0.3 MB

Requires: Win All

image

Keep watch of all those who are in your wireless network with Wireless Network Watcher. Wireless Network Watcher lets you monitor your network to make sure only authorized persons are using your connection.

This program will output the local IP address, the MAC address of devices connected to your network, the manufacturer of the network card the device is using and the name of the device connected.


What's NEW:

Updated the internal MAC addresses database.
